Package org.moeaframework.problem.misc

package org.moeaframework.problem.misc
Set of unconstrained and constrained numeric multiobjective test problems aggregated by Van Veldhuizen [1]. Coello Coello et al. [2] also refer to this list of test problems.

References:

  1. Van Veldhuizen, D. A (1999). "Multiobjective Evolutionary Algorithms: Classifications, Analyses, and New Innovations." Air Force Institute of Technology, Ph.D. Thesis, Appendix B.
  2. Coello Coello, C.A. et al. "Evolutionary Algorithms for Solving Multi-Objective Problems." 2nd Edition, Springer, 2007.
